n A driver maintains a connection pool for each remote Neo4j server. Therefore,\n the most efficient way to make use of a Driver is to use the same instance\n across the application.\n <p>\n To construct a new Driver, use one of the\n <a href=\"GraphDatabase.html#driver(java.lang.String,org.neo4j.driver.AuthToken)\"><code>GraphDatabase.driver</code></a> methods.\n The <a href=\"https://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc3986\">URI</a> passed to\n this method determines the type of Driver created.\n <br>\n <table border=\"1\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse\">\n     <caption>Available schemes and drivers</caption>\n     <thead>\n         <tr><th>URI Scheme</th><th>Driver</th></tr>\n     </thead>\n     <tbody>\n         <tr>\n             <td><code>bolt</code></td>\n             <td>Direct driver: connects directly to the host and port specified in the URI.</td>\n         </tr>\n         <tr>\n             <td><code>neo4j</code></td>\n             <td>Routing driver: can automatically discover members of a Causal Cluster and route <a href=\"Session.html\" title=\"interface in org.neo4j.driver\"><code>sessions</code></a> based on <a href=\"AccessMode.html\" title=\"enum class in org.neo4j.driver\"><code>AccessMode</code></a>.</td>\n         </tr>\n     </tbody>\n </table></div>\n</section>\n<\n--- org.neo4j.driver/org/neo4j/driver/GraphDatabase.html\nss=\"type-signature\"><span class=\"modifiers\">public final class </span><span class=\"element-name type-name-label\">GraphDatabase</span>\n<span class=\"extends-implements\">extends <a href=\"https://docs.oracle.com/en/java/javase/17/docs/api/java.base/java/lang/Object.html\" title=\"class or interface in java.lang\" class=\"external-link\">Object</a></span></div>\n<div class=\"block\">Creates <a href=\"Driver.html\" title=\"interface in org.neo4j.driver\"><code>drivers</code></a>, optionally letting you <a href=\"#driver(java.net.URI,org.neo4j.driver.Config)\"><code>driver(URI, Config)</code></a> to configure them.</div>\n<dl class=\"notes\">\n<dt>Since:</dt>\n<dd>1.0</dd>\n<dt>See Also:</dt>\n<dd>\n<ul class=\"see-list\">\n<li><a href=\"Driver.html\" title=\"interface in org.neo4j.driver\"><code>Driver</code></a></li>\n</ul>\n</dd>\n</dl>\n</section>\n<section class=\"summary\">\n<ul class=\"summary-list\">\n<!-- ========== METHOD SUMMARY =========== -->\n<li>\n<section class=\"method-summary\" id=\"method-summary\">\n<h2>Method Summary</h2>\n<div id=\"method-summary-table\">\n<div class=\"table-tabs\" role=\"tablist\" aria-orientation=\"horizontal\"><button id=\"method-summary-table-tab0\" role=\"tab\" aria-selected=\"true\" aria-controls=\"method-summary-table.tabpanel\" tabindex=\"0\" onkeydown=\"switchTab(event)\" onclick=\"show('method-summary-table', 'method-summary-table', 3)\" class=\"active-table-tab\">All Methods</button><button id=\"method-summary-table-tab1\" role=\"tab\" aria-selected=\"false\" aria-controls=\"method-summary-table.tabpanel\" tabind\n"}], "isError": false, "timestamp": 1782741321518}, {"role": "toolResult", "toolCallId": "call_CB49qdJPD6QQbM0asSTeD18A|fc_0c9f1799c1d856c8016a427948a578819395ec499bf57e7e59", "toolName": "bash", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "org/neo4j/driver/ObjectMappingTests$PrivateRecord.class\norg/neo4j/driver/stress/AbstractStressTestBase$ResourcesInfo.class\norg/neo4j/driver/stress/SingleInstanceStressIT$Context.class\norg/neo4j/driver/stress/CausalClusteringStressIT$Context.class\norg/neo4j/driver/stress/SessionPoolingStressIT$Worker.class\norg/neo4j/driver/integration/SessionResetIT$1.class\norg/neo4j/driver/integration/GraphDatabaseAuthClusterIT$23.class\norg/neo4j/driver/integration/GraphDatabaseAuthDirectIT$7.class\norg/neo4j/driver/integration/GraphDatabaseAuthClusterIT$1.class\norg/neo4j/driver/integration/GraphDatabaseAuthDirectIT$8.class\norg/neo4j/driver/integration/GraphDatabaseAuthDirectIT$23.class\norg/neo4j/driver/integration/ErrorIT.class\norg/neo4j/driver/integration/GraphDatabaseAuthDirectIT$2.class\norg/neo4j/driver